NKRS - m-Suffix of pT

The data item records the unspecified multiplicity of multiple primary tumours at a single site.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-crl/CodeSystem/nkrs-msuffixofpt
